  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/97f61dfad2979af392b270ec645bc0ab.poster.avif?t=1771160140\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/97f61dfad2979af392b270ec645bc0ab.webm?t=1771160140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/97f61dfad2979af392b270ec645bc0ab.mp4?t=1771160140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the lifechanging, inspiring and mindblowing gameplay of Staring Contest, and becoming an unstoppable, professional starer in the process. Game contains 7 opponents, ranging in difficulty and trickery. Will your opponent's stare prove too hard?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Staring Contest is an odyssey, a tearless journey into the abyss of the human soul. It's the game you didn't know you needed until now.\" - Alberto</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/3e695b90f6a3f581dc06747009dfde39.poster.avif?t=1771160140\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/3e695b90f6a3f581dc06747009dfde39.webm?t=1771160140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2622200/extras/3e695b90f6a3f581dc06747009dfde39.mp4?t=1771160140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Opponents featured:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alberto👨</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pepito🧒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mr. Skeleton AKA Skelly💀🦴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moai🗿</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potato🥔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lizard🦎</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish (Fish)🐟</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck on your journey! You will need it!</p>",
